## 💡 Key Concepts
- `variables:` block supports inline values and group references
- `- group:` links a Library variable group
- `parameters:` enables runtime dropdowns when triggering manually
- `##vso[task.setvariable]` sets variables dynamically between steps
- Secret variables are **always masked** in pipeline logs
